A reader and graphic display of the data from the Vuzix Wrap 920AR tracker.

Usage:
    for reading from the tracker: 
        ./run
    this also creates .txt and .png data in the graphs folder
    by default it reads from /dev/hidraw0, but can also accept a device name as an argument
    
    graphs of .txt data can be replayed with:
        python Graph.py < graphs/data.txt
    and .png images recreated with:
        python Graph.py -png < graphs/data.txt

Requirements:
    gcc
    python
    python-pygame
    scrot
